OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fkiller's death will lead to
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fbody find                  
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A woman whose daughter was murdered has
OL,6, said she hopes the death of the killer 
OL,7, will mean she will finally find out    
OL,8, what happened to her remains.          
OL,10,FIan Simms, who died recently, was      
OL,11,Fjailed in 1989 for Helen McCourt's     
OL,12,Fmurder, but never revealed where her   
OL,13,Fbody was and was released in 2020.     
OL,15,FMarie McCourt, who campaigned for a    
OL,16,Fparole law change, said she hoped he   
OL,17,Fhad told someone in jail where she was.
OL,19,FShe added that hearing of Simms' death 
OL,20,Fwas "the best news I've had".          
